	<element name="Aka Oni (Red Oni)" type="Sub Race" source="Homebrew" id="ID_HOMEBREW_SUB_RACE_RED_ONI">
		<supports>Oni</supports>
		<description>
			<p>The most common out of the oni, red oni or aka oni are known for their large size and toughness. They are slightly bigger than the rest of their kin, with skin coloration in shades of dark red. They are violent, hot-headed, and unfocused, often pursuing immediate satisfaction and disregarding long-term plots and schemes.</p>
			<p class="indent"><strong><em>The Revel Continues.</em></strong> When you are reduced to 0 hit points but not killed outright, you can drop to 1 hit point instead. You can’t use this feature again until you finish a long rest. </p>
			<p class="indent"><strong><em>Ability Score Increase.</em></strong> Your Strength score is increased by 1. </p>
		</description>
			<sheet display="false"/>
		<rules>
			<grant type="Racial Trait" id="ID_RACIAL_TRAIT_THE_REVEL_CONTINUES" />
			<stat name="strength" value="1" />
		</rules>
	</element>

