  <element name="Ao Oni (Blue Oni)" type="Sub Race" source="Homebrew" id="ID_SUB_RACE_BLUE_ONI">
		<supports>Oni</supports>
		<description>
			<p>Blue oni or ao oni are known for their unnatural cunning and aptitude for magic. They are smaller than their red kin, though larger than their pale kin, and with skin coloration of shades of dark blue. They are usually calculating and meticulous pursuing lofty goals such as of power and knowledge.</p>
			<p class="indent"><strong><em>Ability Score Increase.</em></strong> Your Inteligence score Increases by 1.</p>
			<p class="indent"><strong><em>Oni Magic.</em></strong>  Blue oni can muster the innate magic within themselves which gets stronger as they grow in power. You know the dancing lights cantrip. When you reach 3rd level, you can cast the charm person spell once and need to finish a long rest before you can cast it again. Intelligence is your spellcasting ability for these spells.</p>
		</description>
		<sheet display="false" />
		<rules>
			<stat name="Inteligence" value="1" />
			<grant type="Racial Trait" id="ID_RACIAL_TRAIT_ONI_MAGIC" />
		</rules>
	</element>

	<element name="Oni Magic" type="Racial Trait" source="Homebrew" id="ID_RACIAL_TRAIT_ONI_MAGIC">
		<description>
			<p> Blue oni can muster the innate magic within themselves which gets stronger as they grow in power. You know the dancing lights cantrip. When you reach 3rd level, you can cast the charm person spell once and need to finish a long rest before you can cast it again. Intelligence is your spellcasting ability for these spells.</p>
		</description>
		<sheet>
			<description level="1">You know the dancing lights cantrip. (Spellcasting: Intelligence)</description>
			<description level="3">You know the dancing lights cantrip and you can cast the charm person spell once and need to finish a long rest before you can cast it again. (Spellcasting: Intelligence)</description>
		</sheet>
		<rules>
			<grant type="Spell" id="ID_PHB_SPELL_DANCING_LIGHTS" level="1" />
			<grant type="Spell" id="ID_PHB_SPELL_CHARM_PERSON" level="3" />
		</rules>
	</element>

	<element name="Shiro Oni (Pale Oni)" type="Sub Race" source="Homebrew" id="ID_SUB_RACE_PALE_ONI">
		<supports>Oni</supports>
		<description>
			<p>Pale oni or shiro oni are known for their aloofness and connections to the spiritual realm. They are the smallest of oni, and are the fewest. Their skin can vary from pale white to light grey. Unlike the other oni, pale oni wish only to keep the balance between the Spirit World and the Material Plane. They usually guard locations where the presence of the Spirit World but sometimes adventure to seek artifacts of the spirit world or mend imbalances.</p>
			<p class="indent"><strong><em>Ability Score Increase.</em></strong>Your Wisdom score is increased by 1.</p>
			<p class="indent"><strong><em>Spirit Walk.</em></strong> Pale oni are still heavily in tune with the spirit world and can for brief moments step through the boundaries between planes. As an action, you can magically teleport up to 30 feet to an unoccupied space of darkness that you can see. Once you use this trait, you can’t do so again until you finish a short or long rest.</p>
		</description>
		<sheet display="false" />
		<rules>
			<stat name="Wisdom" value="1" />
			<grant type="Racial Trait" id="ID_RACIAL_TRAIT_SPIRIT_WALK" />
		</rules>
	</element>

